{
  "texts": [
    "Before extracting the image features in the initial stage, we standardize the image size to 448 × 448 and extract 1 × 1,024 feature tensors using the feature extractor.",
    "These are then saved in an npy file for use in subsequent image caption generation tasks.",
    "It should be noted that there will be multiple diseased regions in an image, and each diseased region will generate a 1 × 1,024 tensor.",
    "Therefore, there will be several tensors in the.npy file corresponding to an image.",
    "The Faster R-CNN model used to extract image features utilizes the Swin Transformer as its backbone."
  ]
}